{"tid":654913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[返工返到失禁]的哥疑病發失禁　昏倒車旁","createTime":"2018-05-06T05:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T05:46:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b29b0158a8f02055dd7c632cdafd1dd64626266","tid":654913,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"旺角海輝道8號近浪澄灣對出，今晨3時52分，一名姓李（48歲）的哥因駕駛期間疑不適，遂將車停於上址往美孚方向一巴士站旁，並通知早更司機到場取車，惟事主疑落車「鬆一鬆」時不支暈倒車旁；有途人發現，以為發生車禍，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方及救護員到場，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現事主失禁</span>，救護員將他送院搶救，其後恢復知覺，但仍需即時接受手術。的哥的1女2男親友接報抵院了解。警方經調查後，事件不涉交通意外，列作有人暈倒處理。<br />\n<br />\n職業司機工時長壓力大、食無定時、又經常捱夜、長期坐在狹小駕駛座上缺乏運動，容易血壓超標、高血糖、肥胖、運動不足等情況，患心臟病的風險及中風會較一般人高，故司機應定期驗身及注意健康<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180506/bkn-20180506043417932-0506_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180506%2Fbkn-20180506043417932-0506_00822_001.html&d=sGwUIirdB4qypkm10ixhJp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=be9319a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180506/bkn-20180506043417932-0506_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f39b8ea9b24010688edd65bd198fcfec0dce75d8","tid":654913,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5120299dfddfb66cd74ff604546ddfbcc8643323","tid":654913,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:22:13.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fbccb4a3ba4c3524e0416f11c54b255beb8dfc","tid":654913,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"TIA<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma